  <main>
    <section class='section'>
      Want to contact me? You can either reach me on one of my <a href='/socials'>socials</a>, or shoot me an email
      if you're more into old-school tech.
    </section>
    <section class='section'>
      <h3 class='underlined'>Email</h3>
      <p>
        Emails in 2022?? Yeah. I read these, and I even reply to them! Except if you're sending me weird stuff or spam.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href='mailto:cynthia@cynthia.dev' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>cynthia@cynthia.dev</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='mailto:cyyynthia@borkenware.com' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>cyyynthia@borkenware.com</a> for
          professional inquiries
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class='section'>
      <h3 class='underlined'>PGP</h3>
      <p>
        You can use PGP to encrypt your emails if you want. Make sure your public key is available somewhere, or I'll
        have to reply in boring plaintext...
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>key: <a href='/pgp.txt' target='_blank'>https://cynthia.dev/pgp.txt</a></li>
        <li>fingerprint: <code class='uppercase'>FDDF 5DD9 34DC 5814 6C8B 3E8B CB56 1F74 DCEA E23B</code></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>
</GlobalLayout>
